questions: If you are interested in the life of fish, you should go to   _  .
article:
Sunny English Club
For students
Open Time: 16:00--18:00   Every Saturday
Tickets: 200 yuan a month
Address: 9 Zhouyu Street
Tel: 3785290
Foreign teachers, English songs and films and more!
Ocean Museum
Open Time: 9:00--17:00   From Thursday to Sunday
Ticket: 50 yuan
Address: 132 Xueyuan Street
Tel: 5439871
Show you a full picture of sea lives!
Health Centre
Time: 9:00-- 17:30
Address: 16 Yongle Street
Tel: 3801451
Free examinations for those over 70. Give you good advice to keep healthy!
